                                    </h3>
                                </div>
                                <div class="panel-body">

                                    <div class="row info-row">
                                        <div class="col-md-5 info-label">Full Name:</div>
                                        <div class="col-md-7">Mr. Stephen Wai</div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="row info-row">
                                        <div class="col-md-5 info-label">Email:</div>
                                        <div class="col-md-7">yo@stephenwai.com</div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="row info-row">
                                        <div class="col-md-5 info-label">Address: </div>
                                        <div class="col-md-7">645 Harrison St<br>San Francisco, CA 94107</div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="row info-row">
                                        <div class="col-md-5 info-label">Mobile Phone:</div>
                                        <div class="col-md-7">(555) 555-5555</div>
                                    </div>
